## User Journeys (Step by Step)

### Journey 1: New member shares a problem
Welcome → Sign up → Tutorial (3 steps) → Home → Tap “New Post” → Write story → Optionally add photo → Choose anonymous or named → Post → Story appears in feed → Others comment and like → Author sees notifications and reader count on profile.

### Journey 2: Supporting someone else
Home → Read story → Like or bookmark → Open comments → Reply → Author gets notified.

### Journey 3: Managing privacy
Profile → Settings → Privacy & Security → Toggle options → Change password or export data.

### Journey 4: Finding content
Home → Search → Type keyword or tap trending topic → Open story from results.

### Journey 5: Learning break
Bottom nav → Fun Activities → Pick activity → Opens in browser.

