## Technical Stack

### Mobile app (frontend)

| Layer | Technology |
|-------|------------|
| Framework | React Native 0.86 |
| Language | TypeScript 5.8 |
| UI library | React 19 |
| Navigation | React Navigation 7 (native stack) |
| Icons | Lucide React Native |
| Safe areas | react-native-safe-area-context |
| State | React Context (global app state) |
| Local persistence | AsyncStorage (auth session + login cache) |

### Content & media

| Capability | Technology |
|------------|------------|
| Rich text editing | TenTap Editor (HTML output) |
| Photo/video picker | react-native-image-picker |
| Video playback | react-native-video |
| HTML rendering | Custom lightweight HTML parser |
| Date/time scheduling | react-native-date-picker |
| Web content | react-native-webview (editor dependency) |

### Backend & infrastructure

| Service | Role |
|---------|------|
| **Supabase** | Primary backend |
| Supabase Auth | Email/password login, sessions, password reset |
| Supabase PostgreSQL | All app data (stories, profiles, likes, etc.) |
| Supabase Storage | Public buckets for post images and videos |
| Row Level Security (RLS) | Database rules: who can read/write what |
| SQL views | Aggregated story stats (likes, comments, readers) |
| Database triggers | Auto-create profile and settings on signup |
| RPC functions | Account deletion cascade |

### Configuration & tooling

| Tool | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| react-native-dotenv | Environment variables (API URL, keys) |
| react-native-url-polyfill | URL compatibility for Supabase |
| Jest | Testing scaffold |
| ESLint + Prettier | Code quality |
| Node.js ≥ 22.11 | Runtime requirement |

### Platforms
- **Android** (Gradle build, native launcher icons)
- **iOS** (Xcode project, app icons)

### Not integrated
