## Design & UX Patterns

**Visual identity**
- Light theme: white backgrounds, dark slate text, yellow primary buttons
- Rounded cards, bold headings, soft gray borders
- Circular Haven logo (hands/community imagery) on auth and home

**Interaction patterns**
- Sensitive content: tap to reveal
- Comments: slide-up bottom sheet
- Avatar: modal grid picker
- Scheduled posts: purple “Scheduled” badge; tap opens edit
- Optimistic like/bookmark updates
- Custom bottom bar on main screens (not a system tab navigator)

**Auth UX**
- Cached login for faster return
- Brief white screen while session restores
- Logged-in users skip login stack

