## Haven vs Typical Social Apps

| Typical social app | Haven |
|-------------------|--------|
| Photo/video first | **Text and story first** |
| Real names/photos common | **Avatars + anonymous option** |
| Algorithmic feed | **Chronological feed** |
| Public by default | **Sensitive blur, comment toggles, scheduling** |
