## Layman’s Glossary

| Term | Plain meaning |
|------|----------------|
| Story | A post someone writes—like a blog entry or diary share |
| Anonymous | Others see “Anonymous User,” not your real name |
| Sensitive content | Blurred until you choose to view it |
| Bookmark / Save | Private list of stories you want to keep |
| Reader count | How many different people opened your story (not you) |
| Scheduled post | Written now, published automatically later |
| Fun Activities | Links to educational games and learning sites |
| Notification | In-app alert when someone interacts with your content |
| Avatar | A fun icon representing you instead of a photo |

